Module it.polimi.ingsw.gc19
Package it.polimi.ingsw.gc19.Networking.Client.Message

Class MessageHandler

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
it.polimi.ingsw.gc19.Networking.Client.Message.MessageHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
AnswerToActionMessageVisitor, AllMessageVisitor, NotifyChatMessageVisitor, ConfigurationMessageVisitor, GameEventsMessageVisitor, GameHandlingMessageVisitor, MessageToClientVisitor, NetworkHandlingErrorMessageVisitor, TurnStateMessageVisitor, Runnable
public class MessageHandler extends Thread implements AllMessageVisitor
This class is responsible for visiting all messages (excluding heartbeats) received from the network. If necessary, it updates LocalModel and notifies ClientController. Its implementation is strongly based on visitor design pattern.
